title: Bankstown Basketball Stadium
text: Bankstown Basketball Stadium is an Australian basketball centre in Bankstown, <a href="New%20South%20Wales">New South Wales</a>. The eight-court arena was the home of NBL side <a href="Bankstown%20Bruins">Bankstown Bruins</a> until 1985 before renaming West Sydney Westars and returned in 1988.
